## Boot Protocol

1. Check `.sovereign/session_state.json` for `warm_start_valid`
2. Verify `.sovereign/topology_fingerprint.txt` matches current TOPOLOGY.md + ARCHITECTURE_MAP.md
3. If warm: read PROVENANCE.md Session Log, confirm last action
4. If cold or stale: full BOOT_PROTOCOL.md Section 2 discovery sequence
5. After any substantive work: update PROVENANCE.md Session Log via `session-close`

