## Available Tools

Claude Code tools permitted by `.claude/settings.json`:
- Bash(python:*) — run Python scripts
- Read(*) — read any file
- Write(src/**), Write(tests/**) — write in src and tests
- Bash(go build:*) — build Go if applicable

**Prohibited:**
- Bash(rm -rf:*) — destructive operations require explicit confirmation
- Write(manifest.json) — snapshot files are read-only by doctrine

